FROM title t, movie_companies mc, cast_info ci
WHERE t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.kind_id  >  1 AND mc.company_id  =  18156 AND mc.company_type_id  =  1 AND ci.person_id  <  620160 AND ci.role_id  >  1
